QuestData.Title: To Skold-Ashil
QuestData.Description:
Thanks to your initiative, $c, the situation at Dreadwake's Landing is under control. We have no time to rest on our laurels, however - Sylvanas's mission must still be carried out.
The dark rangers are heading up operations in Skold-Ashil from the tower overlooking the river junction. Seek them out there, and see if you can aid in completing this task.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet with the dark rangers in Ranger's Foothold, outside of Skold-Ashil.
